{"tid":999694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要求兒子優先求醫    大媽推跌廣華姑娘","createTime":"2019-01-29T01:44:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T07:12:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"57b78a219d73fd9f0e3426807adaef15ca90c5bf","tid":999694,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190129/large/1548719417_e2c2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190129%2Flarge%2F1548719417_e2c2.jpg&h=3aeadd6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名持身份證帶內地口音的41歲女子，帶同年約7歲、疑喉嚨痛的兒子，到旺角廣華醫院急症室求醫，經分流後並不屬於緊急，據知有人多次擅自進入診療室，並大吵大鬧，要求先讓其兒子看醫生。<br />\n<br />\n至凌晨約3時半，她再次吵鬧時，推跌上前勸阻的45歲姓羅姑娘，羅姑娘墮地後手部受傷，於是通知駐院警員，警員以涉嫌襲擊拘捕該女子，並召警車將她帶走。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190129/59197097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197097&d=AMPtd42ADahZ7WU%2BVKQ9tcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=bebae4b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190129%2F59197097&h=075672a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190129/59197097</a>"},{"pid":"e4d7bbd5c2fe81d0a72834393cfff35079f3e54c","tid":999694,"uid":113000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:45:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b2eaa0343c2ce9fcb507938c74d8410af56407","tid":999694,"uid":4180,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:46:28.000Z","msg":"躝啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5786580fd1e97d97058f4e52ad6ccfbd2fb52eb","tid":999694,"uid":61748,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T01:47:20.